description:
From the Deep South, Keegan stands tall at 6 feet. 

“Has anyone ever told you that you have a great accent?” I had to ask.
“Yeah I get that a ton actually.” 
He said with a southern accent.
 “Its funny actually, I’m not the best at flirting so it helps me with my game.”

Keegan spends most of his time trying to eat healthy and work out as much as possible. 
“I like the dedication it takes and the satisfaction of seeing my body look more and more in shape! It’s a turn on for sure.”
title: Keegan
